title: Innovation Expo at NYCDA
desc: We have a fresh batch of students completing our Web Development Intensive program, and we invite you to check them out at our Innovation Expo! ? ? Throughout our 12 week program, we transform beginners into experienced developers. The project based courses immerse our students in many different areas: Web Development Join us at our headquarters to meet the graduates and speak with them about their work. They'll have projects setup for demonstration, along with resumes to take with you.
